Mansour Hadi, Prime Minister Abdul-Karim al-Iryani, Speaker of the
Consultative Council Abdul-Aziz Abdul-Ghani, Secretary General of
Yemeni presidency Abdulla el-Bashiri, Minister of Construction,
Housing and Urban Planning Abdullah Hussain al-Dafe'e, Sanaa Mayor
Hussein el-Masoury, and Chinese Ambassador to Yemen Zhu Guobin.
