<HEADLINE> People's Daily Hails 10th Anniversary of Pudong's Opening (2) </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Priority has been given to building infrastructure projects and
developing financial, trade and hi-tech industries in Pudong,
while attention has been paid to cultural advance.
</P>
<P>
Pudong has pioneered a series of reforms including open bidding
for construction projects and government procurement to curb
corruption, which is also proven successful, the paper says.
</P>
<P>
Shanghai's experience in developing and opening up Pudong over
the past decade will continue to play a guiding role for Pudong's
development in the next ten years and provide a model for
developing China western regions, it says.  
