cents to 23.8 Australian dollars after a good run in recent days
while the Commonwealth Bank powered 69.6 cents higher to 24.97
Australian dollars.
</P>
<P>
ANZ was up 16 cents to 11.45 Australian dollars.
</P>
<P>
National turnover was 720 million shares worth 1.9 billion
Australian dollars (1.18 billion U.S. dollars) with 117 falls, 524
rises and 428 stocks steady. 
</P>
