<TEXT>
<P>
ATHENS, April 13 (Xinhua) -- Greece's new cabinet, led by Prime
Minister Costas Simitis, was sworn in on Thursday following the
ruling Panhellenic Socialist Movement's victory in Sunday's
parliamentary elections.
</P>
