for its "experience and renewal."
</P>
<P>
After the ceremony, the new cabinet held its first meeting.
</P>
<P>
The new cabinet is made up of 20 ministers, 22 deputy ministers
and one alternate minister while the previous cabinet was composed
of 19 ministers, 21 deputy ministers and one alternate minister.
