patacas (about 9.62 million U.S. dollars) and are expected to
create more than 720 new jobs, Lee said, adding that another 10
projects are undergoing procedures of approval.
</P>
<P>
He noted that better investment services have been provided to
investors since the establishment of the SAR in last December. And
a special investment committee comprising members from 10
government departments has been set up.
</P>
<P>
Lee Peng Hong also acts as the head of the 10-member committee.
In this sense, the institute can make more efficient contacts with
various government departments and investors do not have to go
through procedures one after another all by themselves.  
