<HEADLINE> Telecommunications: Priority in West Development (2) </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Sichuan Province plans to complete a 3.5-billion-yuan
investment in communication network construction and multi-media
facilities this year.
</P>
<P>
Massive construction of railway and highway projects in Guizhou
Province has greatly stimulated demands for telecommunication
services. Fixed-asset investment worth 800 million yuan will be
put into network construction to double the province's
communication service capacity this year.
</P>
