of communications products for the western regions. The president
of a Shanghai telecommunication company said that the company
never dreamed of investing in the western regions before. But when
he heard that the Ministry of Communications would invest 700
billion yuan in building railways and highways in the west, he
realized that the western regions is fast becoming a cash cow.
