<HEADLINE> Int'l Eye Disease Forum Opens in Shanghai </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
SHANGHAI, April 13 (Xinhua) -- Asia's first international forum
on eye conditions such as nearsightedness, farsightedness and
astigmatism opened today in Shanghai.
</P>
<P>
