officers from all nations of the multi-national troops.
</P>
<P>
Brigadier General Amilkare Casalotto took the power of
commanding the troops as well as the flag from his predecessor
Brigadier General Luigi Chiavarelli, sent by Italy last September,
at an airport in Tirana.
</P>
