<HEADLINE> Slovenian Police Seize Marijuana </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
ZAGREB, April 12 (Xinhua) -- Slovenian customs officers seized
500 kilograms of marijuana Wednesday in the port city of Koper,
the Bosnian news agency quoted Slovenian television as reporting.
</P>
<P>
The drug was hidden in an Albanian truck, which came from
Durres, the largest port of Albania, and was bound for the
Netherlands.
</P>
<P>
The driver, a man of Albanian nationality, was arrested by
Slovenian police. 
