<HEADLINE> Shanghai Financial Units Grant More Loans In March </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
SHANGHAI, April 13 (Xinhua) -- Shanghai's financial
institutions granted 10.67 billion yuan in loans in March.
</P>
<P>
