<HEADLINE> Leading English Premier League Scorers </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
LONDON, April 12 (Xinhua) -- Following are the leading scorers
in the English premier league after Wednesday's matches:
</P>
<P>
27 - Kevin Phillips (Sunderland)
</P>
<P>
19 - Alan Shearer (Newcastle United), Andy Cole (Manchester
United)
</P>
